The Bitcoin Segwit2x fork quietly passed. The network is not usable, so Coinbase will not be supporting this asset.

With this release, we've made a few improvements we think you'll love:
- Improved buy / sell confirmation pages
- Alerts

Thank you for joining us on this journey! We’re constantly working to bring you a better experience on the Coinbase app. With this release, we’ve made a few updates we think you’ll love:

- New feature to easily understand and increase investment

Segwit is coming soon. As we roll this out, please be aware that you should only send BCH to your BCH wallet and BTC to your BTC wallet. After Segwit, we will not be able to recover funds sent to incorrect wallets / addresses.

Segwit is coming soon. As we roll this out, please be aware that you should only send Bitcoin Cash (BCH) to your BCH wallet and Bitcoin (BTC) to your BTC wallet. After Segwit, we will not be able to recover funds sent to incorrect wallets / addresses. <br
